                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>will yet send their Mite</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Excuse scrawl</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">In Haste yours Truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Isaac Hart</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p><persName>Mr M Goldsmith</persName> has just<lb/> lost one of his children<lb/>\n                <persName>Annie</persName> aged 5 years<lb/> and I fear ere 24 Hours he<lb/> will\n                lose his only son<lb/> the Doctors fear the worst</p>\n            <p>I never knew so much sickness<lb/> in those Born here</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
